Kalau begitu ada yg selamat waktu itu?

00:13:37.420 --> 00:13:39.040
Sepertinya begitu...

00:13:39.580 --> 00:13:41.550
Apa dia juga akan mati?

00:13:41.550 --> 00:13:43.070
Susah dikatakan demikian.

00:13:43.070 --> 00:13:45.670
Bisa juga artinya kalau
dia hanya berlumuran darah.

00:13:46.460 --> 00:13:50.420
